%% Data Flow Diagram: odh-model-controller
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>8081/TCP Health, 8080/TCP Metrics
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Service<br/>8080/TCP
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over User,Predictor: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment (RawDeployment Mode)
    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate InferenceService<br/>9443/TCP TLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Event (InferenceService created)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create {isvc}-metrics Service<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor/PodMonitor<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Metrics Dashboard ConfigMap<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create KEDA TriggerAuthentication<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Predictor: Inference Request Flow
    User->>Router: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS Edge/Reencrypt
    Router->>Predictor: Forward request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP or HTTPS

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService Auth Policy Setup
    User->>K8sAPI: POST LLMInferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate LLMInferenceService<br/>9443/TCP TLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Event (LLMInferenceService created)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (Gateway target)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (HTTPRoute target)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter (Gateway TLS)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,NGC: Flow 3: NIM Account Reconciliation
    User->>K8sAPI: POST NIM Account CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate NIM Account<br/>9443/TCP TLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Event (NIM Account created)
    Controller->>NGC: Validate API Key & Fetch Model Catalog<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, Auth: NGC API Key
    NGC-->>Controller: Model Catalog Response
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (model config)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Image Pull Secret<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServingRuntime Templates<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Data Connection Secret Aggregation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create data connection Secret<br/>(via ODH Dashboard)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Event (labeled Secret)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Read all labeled Secrets in namespace<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update storage-config Secret<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Controller,ModelReg: Optional: Model Registry Sync
    Controller->>ModelReg: Sync InferenceService metadata<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, Auth: Bearer Token
    ModelReg-->>Controller: Model metadata response
